 Purpose
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy governs the operational monitoring,
 measurement,
 and reporting of service level performance for the Elko County Information Operations Department.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection*

\lang english
2.
 Scope
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy applies to all Information Operations personnel involved in service delivery,
 triage,
 escalation,
 vendor coordination,
 or performance reporting.
 County Department Heads hold limited review and feedback obligations as defined in Section 3.
