 the Assistant IT Director shall document the vendor failure separately from the IT breach record.
 The Assistant IT Director shall maintain vendor performance data as defined in Section 6.5.
 The Assistant IT Director shall escalate sustained vendor SLA failures to the vendor compliance framework under 
\series bold
Policy 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
