 all open SLA Breaches in active remediation,
 and any Threshold 2 formal reviews in progress.
 Distribution is internal to Information Operations Personnel.
 The Assistant IT Director shall retain this report for a minimum of two (2) calendar years from the year created,
 in accordance with LRDA 20071558.
\end_layout

